    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Between 0 and 18 years of age.

          -  Either severe sepsis, shock of any origin or asphyxia.

          -  Operated patients with operative or post-operative transfusion requirement of at least
             0.5 x 80 ml/kg body weight of erythrocyte concentrate.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Existing affection of the kidney.

          -  Kidney transplantation.

          -  Missing written consent of the parents or guardian (if applicable).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
